  },
  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, the first sip of cardamom chai in the evening makes my day brighter. I heard you're planning to watch 'Chhichhore' this weekend — excited about it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, heard the movie is good. Chai is always a good start, but I still can't unsee the mess I did at work today. Typical Monday, you know?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right, movies are a good escape. Mondays do have a way of tripping us up. What went wrong?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I was sending an email to a client and accidentally hit \"reply all\" to a joke about cricket. My boss saw it and asked if I was taking it seriously. Bhaiya, you know how it goes — sometimes you want to laugh but can't."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Cricket jokes can be tricky in emails — I get it. Work has a way of making us serious even when we want to be light. How did you handle it?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I just said I was sorry and told them it was a mistake. Boss said I need to be more careful. It’s not even a big joke, but now I feel like I messed up. 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right — apologies are a safe bet. Work has a way of making small things feel big. What do you usually do to stay calm in these moments?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I take a deep breath and step away for a bit. Sometimes I listen to a song or two. It helps. But honestly, it’s hard not to feel frustrated. 😒"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Stepping away is smart — music or quiet time helps. Frustration is normal when we feel on edge. What song do you turn to when you need to reset?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Ed Sheeran’s ‘Photograph’ or maybe a random Bollywood song. Anything that’s not too intense. It’s just hard sometimes to switch modes when you’re already stressed, you know?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Same — soft songs help slow things down. Stress makes it tricky to switch gears. Did you watch 'Chhichhore' yet, or is it still tomorrow?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Still tomorrow. Planning to watch it after work. Maybe it'll take my mind off the emails and cricket jokes for a while. Let me just survive today first, you know? 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right — tomorrow’s a fresh start. Chhichhore is a good escape. What’s your plan to survive today?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Finish my tasks one by one. Maybe some tea and deep breaths in between. If another mistake happens, it happens. Just not let it eat my day. 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Tea and deep breaths — solid plan. Mistakes happen, but it’s how we move on that matters. What’s the first task on your list?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "First task is replying to those emails I kept putting off. Slowly, without any more jokes. 😅 But first, another cup of tea — maybe it’ll give me some courage. Or at least warmth."
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right — tea warms up courage in small sips. What’s the email about?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It’s about a payment gateway integration. I have to explain some technical stuff to the client. Not complicated, but I need to make sure it’s clear and not too jargon-heavy. Sometimes I overthink it — it’s like trying to explain cricket rules to a non-fan. Runs, wickets, what’s the point? 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right — jargon can feel like a different language. Cricket rules do baffle some! What part do you find trickiest to explain?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The part where I have to simplify technical terms without sounding too casual. Like, I don’t want to sound unprofessional, but also don’t want to confuse them. It’s like trying to balance a wicket while not dropping the ball. 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Good parallel — balancing is tricky! What’s one term you recently had to explain clearly?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "APIs. I had to explain how one app talks to another without using ‘middleware’ or ‘endpoint’ — ended up comparing it to a waiter taking an order between two tables. Not perfect, but they seemed to get it. Phew."
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right — the waiter analogy is relatable. It’s all about making it click in simple terms. What’s next on your list?\""
    }
  ],
